&lt;p&gt;在任意一个 mq 控制台查看队列：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PigPigLetsGo/imeages/master/202310221140517.png&#34; alt=&#34;image-20210717231829505&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
